{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make defibrillators mandatory in all types of gym or exercise establishments",
        "additional_details": "With over 90% of sudden cardiac arrests in young athletes occurring during or just after exercise, a readily available AED can increase survival rates from near 0% to 50-70% if used within 3\u20135 minutes of a cardiac arrest.",
        "background": "Make it a legal requirement for defibrillators to be available in all types of gym or exercise establishment.",
